6 And Esau saw that Isaac blessed Jacob, and sent him away to Mesopotamia of Syria as he blessed him, to take to himself a wife thence, and <FI>that<Fi> he charged him, saying, Thou shalt not take a wife of the daughters of the Chananites;
7 and <FI>that<Fi> Jacob hearkened to his father and his mother, and went to Mesopotamia of Syria.
8 And Esau also having seen that the daughters of Chanaan were evil before his father Isaac,
