8 And ye shall offer whole-burnt-offerings to the Lord seven days; and the seventh day shall be <RF><i>Or</i>, called holy. See Rom. 1:7.<Rf>a holy convocation to you: ye shall do no servile work.
9 And the Lord spoke to Moses, saying,
