3 blessed <FI>shalt<Fi> thou <FI>be<Fi> in the city, and blessed shalt thou be in the field.
4 Blessed shall be the offspring of thy <RF><i>Gr.</i> belly.<Rf>body, and the fruits of thy land, and the herds of thy oxen, and the flocks of thy sheep.
