1 <T>For the end, concerning the people that were removed from the <RF><i>Or</i>, holy things.<Rf>sanctuary, by David for a memorial, when the Philistines caught him in Geth.<t><CM>Have mercy upon me, O God; for man has trodden me down; all the day long he warring has afflicted me.
